---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Website Content Dashboard | Jake Fixes Tech — Littleton, NH"
description="Update your own website without calling a developer. Jake Fixes Tech offers a secure content dashboard add-on for all website packages. Edit text, swap images and go live in 60 seconds.">

  <!-- Header -->
  <section style="position:relative;overflow:hidden;background-color:rgb(30,64,175);">
    <img src="/hero.jpg" alt="Professional tech workspace with dual monitors" style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;z-index:0;" />
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(30,64,175,0.88),rgba(37,99,235,0.88));z-index:1;"></div>
    <div style="max-width:56rem;margin:0 auto;padding:5rem 1.5rem 4rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;position:relative;z-index:2;">
      <p style="font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#93c5fd;">Optional Add-On</p>
      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;color:white;margin-top:0.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;">Your Website. Your Dashboard.</h1>
      <p style="color:#bfdbfe;font-size:1.1rem;line-height:1.75;max-width:42rem;margin:0 auto;">Update your own website from any browser without touching a single line of code. Change your hours, swap a photo, update your prices — done in minutes from your phone, tablet or computer.</p>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Is It -->
  <section style="background:white;padding:5rem 1.5rem;">
    <div style="max-width:56rem;margin:0 auto;">
      <p style="font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#2563eb;">What Is It?</p>
      <h2 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;color:#111827;margin-top:0.5rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">A Private Dashboard Built Into Your Website</h2>
      <p style="color:#4b5563;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:1rem;">When I build your website, every word and image is carefully crafted. But things change. Your hours shift, you add a new service, prices go up, you get a better photo. Without a dashboard, every one of those changes means contacting me and waiting.</p>
      <p style="color:#4b5563;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:1rem;">With the Content Dashboard add-on, I build a private editing interface directly into your website. When your site is ready I send you a private login link that only you have. Log in securely with your account and you see a clean dashboard with every editable section of your site laid out in simple form fields.</p>
      <p style="color:#4b5563;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.85;">Change what you need, click Publish, and your website updates automatically — usually within about 60 seconds. No developer. No waiting. No extra charge for the update itself.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works Steps -->
  <section style="background:#f8fafc;padding:4rem 1.5rem;">
    <div style="max-width:56rem;margin:0 auto;">
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:3rem;">
        <p style="font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#2563eb;">How It Works</p>
        <h2 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;color:#111827;margin-top:0.5rem;">Three Steps. No Tech Knowledge Required.</h2>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.5rem;">
        <div style="background:white;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1.5rem;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:1.25rem;">
          <div style="display:flex;height:3rem;width:3rem;min-width:3rem;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border-radius:50%;background:#2563eb;color:white;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:800;flex-shrink:0;">1</div>
          <div>
            <h3 style="font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;color:#111827;margin-bottom:0.375rem;">Open Your Private Login Link</h3>
            <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.7;margin:0;">When your site launches I send you a private link to your dashboard. Bookmark it and use it any time from any device — phone, tablet or computer.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:white;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1.5rem;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:1.25rem;">
          <div style="display:flex;height:3rem;width:3rem;min-width:3rem;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border-radius:50%;background:#2563eb;color:white;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:800;flex-shrink:0;">2</div>
          <div>
            <h3 style="font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;color:#111827;margin-bottom:0.375rem;">Log In Securely</h3>
            <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.7;margin:0;">Your dashboard is protected by secure authentication. Nobody else can access it. One click to log in and you're inside your website's editing interface.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:white;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1.5rem;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:1.25rem;">
          <div style="display:flex;height:3rem;width:3rem;min-width:3rem;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border-radius:50%;background:#2563eb;color:white;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:800;flex-shrink:0;">3</div>
          <div>
            <h3 style="font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;color:#111827;margin-bottom:0.375rem;">Make Changes & Publish</h3>
            <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.7;margin:0;">Every editable section of your site appears as a simple text field or image uploader. Click the field, type your update, click Publish. Your website updates automatically in about 60 seconds.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What You Can Edit -->
  <section style="background:white;padding:4rem 1.5rem;">
    <div style="max-width:56rem;margin:0 auto;">
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:3rem;">
        <p style="font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#2563eb;">What You Can Change</p>
        <h2 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;color:#111827;margin-top:0.5rem;">Edit Anything on Your Pages</h2>
        <p style="color:#6b7280;margin-top:0.75rem;max-width:38rem;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;line-height:1.75;">I define exactly which parts of your site are editable when I build it. Here's what's typically included.</p>
      </div>
      <div id="edit-grid">
        <div class="edit-card">
          <div class="edit-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M11 4H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-7"/><path d="M18.5 2.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L12 15l-4 1 1-4 9.5-9.5z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:700;color:#111827;">All Text & Copy</div>
            <div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#6b7280;margin-top:0.1rem;">Headlines, descriptions, paragraphs, button labels</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="edit-card">
          <div class="edit-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="8.5" r="1.5"/><path d="M21 15l-5-5L5 21"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:700;color:#111827;">Photos & Images</div>
            <div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#6b7280;margin-top:0.1rem;">Upload new images directly from your device</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="edit-card">
          <div class="edit-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:700;color:#111827;">Prices & Services</div>
            <div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#6b7280;margin-top:0.1rem;">Update pricing, add or edit service descriptions</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="edit-card">
          <div class="edit-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:700;color:#111827;">Hours & Contact Info</div>
            <div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#6b7280;margin-top:0.1rem;">Update business hours, phone, email, address</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="edit-card">
          <div class="edit-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M18 8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 7-3 9-3 9h18s-3-2-3-9"/><path d="M13.73 21a2 2 0 0 1-3.46 0"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:700;color:#111827;">Announcements & CTAs</div>
            <div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#6b7280;margin-top:0.1rem;">Change banners, calls to action, promotional text</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="edit-card">
          <div class="edit-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:700;color:#111827;">About & Team Info</div>
            <div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#6b7280;margin-top:0.1rem;">Update your bio, team members, credentials</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top:2rem;background:#fffbeb;border:2px solid #f59e0b;border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:0.75rem;">
        <div style="flex-shrink:0;color:#b45309;margin-top:0.1rem;" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" style="height:1.25rem;width:1.25rem;"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="16" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-width="3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:#92400e;line-height:1.6;margin:0;"><strong>What you can't do from the dashboard:</strong> Add brand new pages, build new sections, or change the design and layout of the site. Those structural changes are what I'm here for — billed at my standard hourly rate. The dashboard is for managing the content that's already there.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Security -->
  <section style="background:#f8fafc;padding:4rem 1.5rem;">
    <div style="max-width:56rem;margin:0 auto;">
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:3rem;">
        <p style="font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#2563eb;">Security</p>
        <h2 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;color:#111827;margin-top:0.5rem;">Only You Can Get In</h2>
        <p style="color:#6b7280;margin-top:0.75rem;max-width:38rem;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;line-height:1.75;">Your dashboard is completely private. The public never sees it and nobody else can access it.</p>
      </div>
      <div id="security-grid">
        <div class="security-card">
          <div class="security-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Secure Login</h3>
          <p>Protected by industry-standard authentication. No username and password to lose or forget.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="security-card">
          <div class="security-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Hidden from the Public</h3>
          <p>Your dashboard is not linked anywhere on your public site. Visitors never know it exists.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="security-card">
          <div class="security-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="23 4 23 10 17 10"/><path d="M20.49 15a9 9 0 1 1-2.12-9.36L23 10"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Every Change is Saved</h3>
          <p>Every edit is version controlled. If something goes wrong I can roll back to any previous version instantly.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section style="background:white;padding:4rem 1.5rem;">
    <div style="max-width:56rem;margin:0 auto;">
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:3rem;">
        <p style="font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#2563eb;">Pricing</p>
        <h2 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;color:#111827;margin-top:0.5rem;">Add a Content Dashboard to Your Build</h2>
        <p style="color:#6b7280;margin-top:0.75rem;max-width:38rem;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;line-height:1.75;">One-time setup fee added to your website build. Must be included at the time of the original build — adding it after launch costs more.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;max-width:40rem;margin:0 auto;">
        <div style="background:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <div>
            <div style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:#111827;">Starter Package Add-On</div>
            <div style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#6b7280;margin-top:0.2rem;">1-3 page websites</div>
          </div>
          <div style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;color:#2563eb;">$100</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:#eff6ff;border:2px solid #2563eb;border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <div>
            <div style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:#111827;">Professional Package Add-On</div>
            <div style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#1e40af;margin-top:0.2rem;">5-15 page websites</div>
          </div>
          <div style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;color:#2563eb;">$250</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <div>
            <div style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:#111827;">Premium Package Add-On</div>
            <div style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#6b7280;margin-top:0.2rem;">30+ pages, quoted by scope</div>
          </div>
          <div style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;color:#2563eb;">$500+</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top:2rem;background:#eff6ff;border:2px solid #bfdbfe;border-radius:0.75rem;padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;max-width:40rem;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">
        <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:#1e40af;line-height:1.6;margin:0;text-align:center;"><strong>Adding a dashboard after your site is already built</strong> requires retrofitting existing pages which takes significantly more time. Always cheaper and faster to include it from the start.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e40af,#2563eb);padding:4rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;">
    <div style="max-width:40rem;margin:0 auto;">
      <h2 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;color:white;margin-bottom:1rem;">Want a Dashboard on Your Website?</h2>
      <p style="color:#bfdbfe;font-size:1.1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:2rem;">Mention it when you reach out and I'll include it in your project quote. It's the best investment you can make if you want to manage your own content going forward.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;gap:1rem;">
        <a href="/contact" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;background:white;color:#2563eb;font-weight:700;padding:0.875rem 2rem;border-radius:0.5rem;text-decoration:none;font-size:1rem;">
          <svg style="height:1.25rem;width:1.25rem;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
          Get in Touch
        </a>
        <a href="/web-services" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);color:white;font-weight:600;padding:0.875rem 2rem;border-radius:0.5rem;text-decoration:none;font-size:1rem;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);">
          View Web Packages
        </a>
      </div>
      <p style="color:#bfdbfe;font-size:0.875rem;margin-top:1.5rem;">
        <a href="/web-services" style="color:#bfdbfe;text-decoration:underline;">Back to Web Services</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  #edit-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 1rem; }
  .edit-card { background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 1.25rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .edit-icon { display: flex; height: 2.5rem; width: 2.5rem; min-width: 2.5rem; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border-radius: 0.5rem; background: #dbeafe; color: #2563eb; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .edit-icon svg { height: 1.25rem; width: 1.25rem; }
  #security-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.25rem; }
  .security-card { background: white; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 1.25rem; text-align: center; }
  .security-icon { display: flex; height: 3rem; width: 3rem; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border-radius: 0.5rem; background: #dbeafe; color: #2563eb; margin: 0 auto 0.75rem auto; }
  .security-icon svg { height: 1.5rem; width: 1.5rem; }
  .security-card h3 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 0.375rem; }
  .security-card p { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    #edit-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    #security-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>